    <item>
      <title>横滨银行考虑再次加息以刺激日本债券市场复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/yokohama-bank-weighs-return-to-japan-bonds-as-boj-set-to-raise-rates-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着利率逐渐上升，日本最大的地区性银行之一渴望恢复购买日本债券，加入到越来越多的金融机构之中，这些机构正在考虑在多年海外投资后重返本地债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/yokohama-bank-weighs-return-to-japan-bonds-as-boj-set-to-raise-rates-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省因成本和收益问题解雇养老金管理委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/alberta-fires-pension-manager-s-entire-board-over-costs-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔投资管理公司 (Alberta Investment Management Corp.) 的整个董事会被省政府解雇，省政府表示，该基金经理已经增加了薪酬和员工，但并未产生可接受的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/alberta-fires-pension-manager-s-entire-board-over-costs-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 21:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
